      "avalancheActivity": {
        "comment": "The main danger will be wet snow avalanches and gliding avalanches. As the weather warms up during the day, the danger of triggering, especially on sunny slopes, will increase significantly.\n\nHowever, there are still many places in the high alpine regions with blown snow where avalanches can be triggered in particular if the load is too high. Weak layers in the snowpack are also a problem. If the load exceeds the load-bearing capacity of the deeper Weak layers, a deep and large avalanche can be triggered. There are many such weak layers, especially on axis above the forest.",
        "highlights": "As the weather warms up, the danger of wet snow avalanches has increased. In the high alpine regions, blowing snow."
